desc: A photo of the famous Hollywood actress, Emma Watson

sttData.content: Emma Watson, born on April 15, 1990, is a British-American actress, activist, and model
sttData.speaker: Narrator

sttData.content: She gained fame for her role as Hermione Granger in the Harry Potter film series and has since starred in various films, including Beauty and the Beast and The Circle
sttData.speaker: Narrator

sttData.content: Watson is also a prominent activist for gender equality
sttData.speaker: Narrator

sttData.content: She is a UN Women Goodwill Ambassador and co-founded the HeForShe campaign
sttData.speaker: Narrator
